1. *Međuvremenu* se već smenilo nekoliko ministara. (In the meantime, several ministers have already been replaced.)

2. U *međuvremenu*, moji prijatelji su se upoznali sa novim ljudima. (In the meantime, my friends got to know new people.)

3. *Međuvremenu*, on je uspeo da obavi svoje poslove. (Meanwhile, he managed to do his tasks.)

4. U *međuvremenu*, mi smo se spremili za put. (In the meantime, we prepared for the trip.)

5. *Međuvremenu*, njega je obuhvatila panika. (Meanwhile, he was seized by panic.)